First activate the environment

    1. source face-recognition-venv/bin/activate

        All the dependency is installed in this.

Then to start flask application run python main.py


Get face features api.

    You need to give base64 image in request payload.

    curl --location --request POST 'http://172.20.10.5:8001/face-feats?image_' \
    --header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
    --data-raw '{
        "image_base64": ""
    }'
